# Frontend Location and Premium Features

## Frontend codebase

All **frontend (UI)** changes for SessionDB belong in **this repository** at:

`/Users/mouli.b/Documents/personal/projects/sessiondb`

Do not add frontend code to the backend/server repo. When asked to implement or change UI, work in this folder.

## Premium features (UI)

Premium feature **components and pages** must live under:

`src/features/Premium/`

- Add new premium feature **screens/components** under `src/features/Premium/` (e.g. `Sessions.tsx`, `Alerts.tsx`, `Reports.tsx` for premium-only pages).
- Register lazy-loaded premium components in `src/features/premium-registry.tsx` and reference them from `App.tsx` via the registry.
- Use `FeatureGate` with the appropriate `featureKey` for routes that require a premium plan; register the feature key in `src/context/AccessContext.tsx` under `currentFeatures` if needed.

## Summary

| What | Where |
|------|--------|
| All frontend code | This repo (sessiondb at the path above) |
| Premium feature UI components | `src/features/Premium/` |
| Premium registry (lazy imports) | `src/features/premium-registry.tsx` |
| Feature flags for premium | `src/context/AccessContext.tsx` → `currentFeatures` |
